item.title: Iron Sky
item.dc:creator: ruisleipa
item.description:
Pokemon Eater:

I hear it’s made in Finland, so whoever saved Finland hated the least during the war would save everyone.

So maybe Americans, as Finland was part of the U.S.S.R. Or maybe the British. :3

Finland has never been a part of the U.S.S.R… Finland became independent from Russia in 1917. The Soviet Union was formed in 1922.

Finland was helped by Germany in World War 2 during the Continuation War that happened after the Winter War. There might have also been some help from some countries during the Winter War, but I can’t name any. The German forces had to be driven out by force as agreed in a deal with the U.S.S.R.

During the cold war Finland tried to remain neutral. It kept itself as a western nation, while still keeping good relations with the U.S.S.R.

(This is what I kinda remember from my history lessons, someone else with deeper knowledge might find serious flaws in my post. )

As to who will be that savior of the world: The whole “USA, the savior of the world” thing seems like a bit of a cliché. Maybe they will use it or not. They might add a fun twist to the old idea, if they are going to use it.

But the movie seems cool. I am going to keep an eye on it.
